    "difficulty": "easy",
    "solution": "Sweetness value order wrt cane sugar\n<br/><br/>Alitame > Sucralose > Saccharin > Aspartame\n<br/><br/>Sucralose = 600\n<br/><br/>Aspartame = 100\n<br/><br/>Saccharin = 550\n<br/><br/>Alitame = 2000",
